11 SECTION 6.(a) G.S. 106-803(a2) reads as rewritten:
12 "(a2) No component of a liquid animal waste management system for which a permit is
13 required under Part 1 or 1A Part 1A of Article 21 of Chapter 143 of the General Statutes, other
14 than a land application site, shall be constructed on land that is located within the 100-year
