23 SEVERABILITY CLAUSE AND EFFECTIVE DATE
24 SECTION 22.(a) If any provision of this act or the application thereof to any person
25 or circumstances is held invalid, such invalidity shall not affect other provisions or applications
26 of this act that can be given effect without the invalid provision or application and, to this end,
27 the provisions of this act are declared to be severable.
28 SECTION 22.(b) Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
29 law.
